						               													<description>Buy, sell, and trade all kinds of crazy mushrooms on your way to victory in this exciting, strategic, and family-friendly card game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;user summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Shroom Shroom is a super fun and strategic card game about collecting and trading all kinds of crazy mushrooms. Players take turns selling, buying, and trading mushrooms to add to their collections. Try and collect different combinations and families of mushrooms to earn points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Choose your cards wisely because you can only have up to ten shrooms in your collection at a time. Some cards have special powers that allow you to develop fun or cruel strategies against each other. The thing that makes Shroom Shroom even more awesome is trading. You can trade anything with anyone at any time during the game. While you're waiting for your turn, make some trades with other players to help build up your collection.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;When the cards run out, everyone adds up their points and the person with the best shroom collection wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
